  "lore": {
    "key": "Tbl_Unit_Desc_174",
    "english": "A monstrosity that looks like a fish. It appears both in the human world and the Demon Realm, disturbing the ecosystem, but its life or origins are still mysterious. Those who have adjusted to the deep seas of the human world are especially fast and fierce, swinging their fins like a blade when hunting.",
